{"type": "article", "id": 29257, "title": "巴黎高定周如火如荼，这里有不少秀场内外的美丽场景", "description": "银色元素正流行。", "date": "2016-07-07T23:07:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1124, "name": "巴黎"}, {"id": 1561, "name": "巴黎高定周"}, {"id": 3018, "name": "高级定制"}, {"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 16821, "name": "Vêtements"}], "category": 19, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160707135048TWXgPBknJrqp97wS.jpg", "contents": "<p>“巴黎高级定制周”是什么，为什么从本周三开始，人们都在谈论它？</p><p>今年一月份，<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/21460.html\">我们曾写过文章介绍“高级定制”（Haute Couture）</a>。高级定制这个词诞生于 150 年前的法国，那时它指的是为皇宫贵族和上流社会制作的服装。发展到现在，高级定制有了一个专门的“高定公会”（Chambre Syndicale de la Couture Parisienne），他们公会设定了一定的标准，符合资质的产品才能被称为高级定制。</p><p>标准主要有以下几个：服装品牌要有自己的工作室（Atelier），工作室至少要有 20 位雇员，他们每年需要举办 2 次高定秀，分别位于 1 月和 7 月，每季系列至少要有 50 件服装，这些服装还必须是手工完成的。</p><p>眼下，巴黎进行的正是 7 月份的高定周，诸如 Chanel, Dior, Versace 等品牌都带来了自己的高定秀。相较于成衣系列，品牌的高定并不怎么赚钱，参加高定更多是为了品牌露出和扬名。从秀场内外的图片可以看出，这一季，繁复的刺绣外套、裤装仍在流行，女士们想穿得优雅又有气场，一身白西装的搭配仍不算过时。</p><p>值得注意的是，不少看秀的人都穿了闪闪发光的银色长裙，银色元素也出现在了诸多品牌的秀场上，估计快时尚品牌的设计师们已经磨刀霍霍，准备在服装上增添银色细节了。</p><p>以下是部分品牌的高定作品：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707132430D97ltsN8mjGiL253.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Backstage at <a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/beauty-features/gallery/backstage-at-jean-paul-gaultier-couture-fall-10482022/packages/10481941/#!26/backstage-at-jean-paul-gaultier-couture-fall-2016-26/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jean Paul Gaultier Couture Fall 2016</a>，图片来源：WWD</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707132507Q9MUbdfE4hK3SmFe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">&nbsp;Jean Paul Gaultier Couture Fall 2016</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707132531qCzr84G5XygFwNkt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Jean Paul Gaultier Couture Fall 2016</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707132644G2l8euZSKDObJAPi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Jean Paul Gaultier Couture Fall 2016</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607071329530Q69ZYHOgANJfLc8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667643\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>Giorgio Armani Privé Couture Fall 2016</p></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707133020OvqDnkQbrZ3Np6yl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>&nbsp;Giorgio Armani Privé Couture Fall 2016<br></p></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707133042QOq0ZR9cdkhDlNzr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>&nbsp;Giorgio Armani Privé Couture Fall 2016</p></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707133107wkp2u1xM5PEYb94G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666179\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>&nbsp;Giorgio Armani Privé Couture Fall 2016</p></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707140047Ewa7hq0H8ISNFzZU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Backstage at Atelier Versace Couture Fall 2016</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707140153fPoY8ejXLkt694xS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Backstage at Atelier Versace Couture Fall 2016</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707140213nR9A3r0DkPIehmwu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Backstage at Atelier Versace Couture Fall 2016</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707140419k18eYu2gqvDcJdfZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Backstage at Atelier Versace Couture Fall 2016</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707140923koeDLqUpjY7ThCRs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>&nbsp;Backstage at Christian Dior Couture Fall 2016</p></figcaption></figure></div><p>除了上面这些传统大牌，今年的巴黎高定周上，值得注意的品牌是<a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/spring-ready-to-wear-2017/paris/vetements/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Vetements</a> 。这个成立于 2 年前的品牌实属后起之秀，却吸引了不少人的眼球，他们那件售价超过 200 美元的带有 “DHL” LOGO 的 T 恤成为了时尚界的爆款。</p><p>这次的巴黎高定周，该品牌以嘉宾身份受巴黎高级时装工会的邀请，他们和 18 个品牌合作，带来了许多“非高定”的作品，继续在时尚的道路上反其道而行之。</p><p>走秀被放在了巴黎老佛爷百货 1 层的走廊上。人们能看到一系列的联名作品，包括 Levi’s、Canada Goose、Reebok、COMME des GARÇONS、Juicy Couture 等，设计灵感源自于街头，充满了运动风。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607071441268MxpcSLUqIfulgzr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501466\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Vetements RTW Spring 2017</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707144226An6WjXRO3l2E17ec.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501466\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Vetements RTW Spring 2017</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707144328XuEmkTwrUpD7OaMl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501466\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Vetements RTW Spring 2017</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707144844r8v1b0RxjIqlNicC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Vestments 大火的 DHL T 恤，权志龙、蕾哈娜都有穿</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">Fashionista 网站给出了一些审美不错的场外穿搭：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707120733hH1xEVDSkwT5fsX6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">巴黎高定周期间的街拍，银色裙装正流行</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607071207575z8QdIOyUNJve7f0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>巴黎高定周期间的街拍，Photo：Emily Malan / Fashionista</p></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707120932EIk0cQanjXDlCOAm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo：Emily Malan / Fashionista</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707120952DGn8wjg1kqJEp6dW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo：Emily Malan / Fashion